[[bench]]
name = "dalek_benchmarks"
harness = false
required-features = [ "alloc", "rand_core",]

[package]
name = "curve25519-dalek"
version = "4.0.0"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.60.0"
authors = [ "Isis Lovecruft <isis@patternsinthevoid.net>", "Henry de Valence <hdevalence@hdevalence.ca>",]
readme = "README.md"
license = "BSD-3-Clause"
repository = "https://github.com/dalek-cryptography/curve25519-dalek"
homepage = "https://github.com/dalek-cryptography/curve25519-dalek"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/curve25519-dalek"
categories = [ "cryptography", "no-std",]
keywords = [ "cryptography", "crypto", "ristretto", "curve25519", "ristretto255",]
description = "A pure-Rust implementation of group operations on ristretto255 and Curve25519"
exclude = [ "**/.gitignore", ".gitignore",]

[dev-dependencies]
bincode = "1"
hex = "0.4.2"
rand = "0.8"

[build-dependencies]
platforms = "3.0.2"
rustc_version = "0.4.0"

[dependencies]
cfg-if = "1"

[features]
default = [ "alloc", "precomputed-tables", "zeroize", "lizard",]
alloc = [ "zeroize?/alloc",]
precomputed-tables = []
legacy_compatibility = []
lizard = [ "digest",]

[dev-dependencies.sha2]
version = "0.10"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.4.0"
features = [ "html_reports",]

[dev-dependencies.rand_core]
version = "0.6"
default-features = false
features = [ "getrandom",]

[dependencies.rand_core]
version = "0.6.4"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.digest]
version = "0.10"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.subtle]
version = "2.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
default-features = false
optional = true
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.zeroize]
version = "1"
default-features = false
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"x86_64\")".dependencies]
cpufeatures = "0.2.6"

[target."cfg(curve25519_dalek_backend = \"fiat\")".dependencies]
fiat-crypto = "0.1.19"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = [ "--html-in-header", "docs/assets/rustdoc-include-katex-header.html", "--cfg", "docsrs",]
features = [ "serde", "rand_core", "digest", "legacy_compatibility",]

[target."cfg(all(not(curve25519_dalek_backend = \"fiat\"), not(curve25519_dalek_backend = \"serial\"), target_arch = \"x86_64\"))".dependencies.curve25519-dalek-derive]
version = "0.1"
path = "../curve25519-dalek-derive"

[package]
name = "curve25519-dalek-derive"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/dalek-cryptography/curve25519-dalek"
homepage = "https://github.com/dalek-cryptography/curve25519-dalek"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/curve25519-dalek-derive"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
description = "curve25519-dalek Derives"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0.66"
quote = "1.0.31"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0.27"
features = [ "full",]

[[bench]]
name = "curve"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "session"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "ratchet"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "sealed_sender"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "kem"
harness = false

[package]
name = "libsignal-protocol"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Signal Messenger LLC",]
edition = "2018"
license = "AGPL-3.0-only"

[dependencies]
aes-gcm-siv = "0.11.1"
arrayref = "0.3.6"
async-trait = "0.1.41"
hkdf = "0.12"
hmac = "0.12"
itertools = "0.10.5"
prost = "0.9"
rand = "0.8"
sha2 = "0.10"
static_assertions = "1.1"
subtle = "2.3"
hex = "0.4"
log = "0.4"
num_enum = "0.6.1"
uuid = "1.1.2"
displaydoc = "0.2"
thiserror = "1.0.30"
pqcrypto-traits = "0.3.4"

[dev-dependencies]
criterion = "0.5"
hex-literal = "0.4.1"
proptest = "1.0"
futures-util = "0.3.7"
env_logger = "0.10.0"

[build-dependencies]
prost-build = "0.9"

[dependencies.signal-crypto]
path = "../crypto"

[dependencies.aes]
version = "0.8.3"
features = [ "zeroize",]

[dependencies.ctr]
version = "0.9.2"
features = [ "zeroize",]

[dependencies.curve25519-dalek]
version = "4.0.0"

[dependencies.x25519-dalek]
version = "2.0.0"
features = [ "static_secrets",]

[dependencies.pqcrypto-kyber]
version = "0.7.6"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

bytes = "1"
derivative = "2.2"

hex = "0.4"
hkdf = "0.12"
hmac = "0.12"
phonenumber = "0.3"
prost = "> 0.10, <= 0.12"
rand = "0.8"
serde_json = "1.0.85"
sha2 = "0.10"

[dependencies.serde]

[dependencies.url]

[dependencies.uuid]

[dependencies.tracing]

[package]
name = "libsignal-service-hyper"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Gabriel Féron <g@leirbag.net>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "AGPL-3.0"
rust-version = "1.70.0"

[dependencies]
async-trait = "0.1"
bytes = "1.0"
futures = "0.3"
tracing = "0.1"

mpart-async = "0.6"

[dev-dependencies]

[features]

[dependencies.libsignal-service]

[dependencies.hyper]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]

[package]

version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Signal Messenger LLC",]

[dependencies]
curve25519-dalek = "4.0"

[package]
